data.description: 3 Bed, 1.1 bath home in the heart of Commerce! Open FamilyRm-Kitchen-Dining room, great for entertaining. Dining room leads to deck overlooking fully fenced backyard with shed, backing up to woods for privacy. Enjoy the real hardwood floors throughout family rm, kitchen, and all 3 bedrooms.  Great location, close to schools, restaurants, shops, and M5/expressways. Walled Lake Schools: Glengary-Walnut Creek-Northern.
